text: The #Coronavirus death count at 46,000 is completely untrustworthy. In a single day, New York added almost 4,000 people—nearly 10% of the total—who never tested positive. With nationwide shenanigans, encouraged by the CDC, one can only guess at the real death count. Shameful!
